  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Problem \r\n\r\nPR https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/pull/14883 introduced a UI regression in the segmented tab component after it was recently merged. The problem was reported by @siddarthkay (here's the original comment https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/pull/14883#discussion_r1095515757).\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n  <thead>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <th><strong>Actual</strong></th>\r\n      <th><strong>Expected</strong></th>\r\n    </tr>\r\n  </thead>\r\n  <tbody>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td><img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/64726664/216557095-3138e860-10be-4e20-a6d6-1228db379d1d.png\" height=\"500\" /></td>\r\n      <td><img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/64726664/216556583-5df32e96-e22a-4c06-8861-bb9ced4623a0.png\" height=\"500\" /></td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n  </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\nGo to `Quo2.0 Preview` > `Segmented`.\r\n\r\n",
